d:
A small gallery of "extremely well endowed on the front" Lalafell. I also turn a lot of other characters into their busty Lalafell form. I intend to be updating this from time to time, when I want to create more. I perfectly might repeat characters (and, obviously, normal Lalafells too).

As a note, considering the general opinion here, I do not consider myself an artist, nor these as art. This are just concepts that AI let me make true where my awful pulse, (total lack of) drawing skills and economy could not. Nothing more, nothing less.
